WAT samples clustering

WAT <- readRDS("mouse_snRNAseq_singlet_removeMTRPHB_WAT_scVI.RDS")
Idents(WAT) = WAT$RNA_snn_res.0.5
#add annotations
new.cluster.ids <- c("Adipocytes", "Stromal cells", "Immune cells", "Stromal cells", "Stromal cells", "Stromal cells", "Vascular cells", "Vascular cells", "Stromal cells", "Stromal cells", "Immune cells", "Stromal cells", "Vascular cells", "Adipocytes", "Stromal cells", "Stromal cells", "Stromal cells")
names(new.cluster.ids) <- levels(WAT)

Figure 7A

WAT_ann <- RenameIdents(WAT, new.cluster.ids)
#change colors and organize clusters
Idents(WAT_ann) <- factor(Idents(WAT_ann),levels = c(grep("Adipocytes",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Adipocytes",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T))],
                                                     grep("Immune cells",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Immune cells",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T))],
                                                     grep("Stromal cells",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Stromal cells",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T))],
                                                     grep("Vascular cells",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Vascular cells",levels(unique(Idents(WAT_ann))),value = T))]
)
)
color_func_blue <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#4785a7", "#266f95")) # Immune cells
color_func_orange <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#F3E55C", "#E8602D")) # Stromal cells
color_func_green <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#7fc39f", "#2E7651")) # Vascular cells
color_func_purp <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#c0acc3", "#907198")) # Adipocytes
p1 <-Stacked_VlnPlot(WAT_ann, features = c("Gls"), log = T, split.by = "Sample_Name", x_lab_rotate = F, colors_use = c("#b08fbf", "#99cc91"), add.noise = F)
cowplot::save_plot("WAT Gls violin plot.pdf", p1, base_height = 4, base_width = 6)
p1

p1.csv <- as.data.frame(p1[[1]][[1]]$data)
head(p1.csv)

WAT adipocytes subclustering (without preadipocytes)

Adipo_WAT <- readRDS("mouse_snRNAseq_singlet_removeMTRPHB_WAT_subnew_scVI.RDS")
Idents(Adipo_WAT) <- Adipo_WAT$RNA_snn_res.0.25
new.cluster.ids <- c("0 White adipocyte", "2 Mt+ adipocyte" ,"1 Beige adipocyte") #add annotations
names(new.cluster.ids) <- levels(Adipo_WAT)
WAT_ann <- RenameIdents(Adipo_WAT, new.cluster.ids)

WT <- subset(x = WAT_ann, subset = Sample_Name %in% "Sample1") #Rename samples
KO <- subset(WAT_ann, subset = Sample_Name %in% "Sample3")
p3 <- ((DimPlot(WT, cols = c("green", "magenta", "purple")) + NoAxes()+ NoLegend() + ggtitle("WT"))+ (DimPlot(KO, cols = c("green", "magenta", "purple"))+NoAxes()+ggtitle("Gls-KO"))) 
p3

cowplot::save_plot("WAT adipocytes DimPlot by sample.pdf", p3, base_height = 5, base_width = 8)

p3.csv <- as.data.frame(rbind(p3[[1]]$data, p3[[2]]$data))

Figure 7B-C

pt <- table(Idents(WAT_ann), WAT_ann$Sample_Name)
pt <- as.data.frame(pt)
pt$Var1 <- as.character(pt$Var1)
count <- 7
getPalette <- colorRampPalette(brewer.pal(8, "Paired"))
p4 <- ggplot(pt, aes(x = Var2, y= Freq, fill = Var1)) +
  theme_bw(base_size = 15) +
  geom_col(position = "fill", width = 0.5) +
  xlab("Sample") +
  ylab("Proportion") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = getPalette(count)) +
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) 

p <- cowplot::plot_grid(p3, p4, ncol = 2, labels = c("WAT adipocytes", "Cluster proportions"), scale = c(1, 0.8))
cowplot::save_plot("WAT adipocytes clustering and proportions.pdf", p, base_height = 5, base_width = 12)
p

p4.csv <- as.data.frame(p4$data)

Figure 7E

BAT <- readRDS("mouse_snRNAseq_singlet_removeMTRPHB_BAT_scVI.RDS")
Idents(BAT) = BAT$RNA_snn_res.0.2
Idents(BAT) <- factor(BAT@active.ident, sort(levels(BAT@active.ident)))
#add annotations
new.cluster.ids <- c("Adipocytes", "Vascular and perivascular cells", "Stromal cells", "Adipocytes", "Immune cells", "Vascular and perivascular cells", "Immune cells", "Stromal cells", "Stromal cells", "Vascular and perivascular cells")

names(new.cluster.ids) <- levels(BAT)
BAT_ann <- RenameIdents(BAT, new.cluster.ids)

Idents(BAT_ann) <- factor(Idents(BAT_ann),levels = c(grep("Adipocytes",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Adipocytes",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T))],
                                                     grep("Immune cells",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Immune cells",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T))],
                                                     grep("Stromal cells",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Stromal cells",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T))],
                                                     grep("Vascular",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T)[order(grep("Vascular",levels(unique(Idents(BAT_ann))),value = T))]
)
)
color_func_blue <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#4785a7", "#266f95")) # Immune cells
color_func_orange <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#F3E55C", "#E8602D")) # Stromal cells
color_func_green <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#7fc39f", "#2E7651")) # Vascular cells
color_func_purp <- colorRampPalette(colors = c("#c0acc3", "#907198")) # Adipocytes

Subclustering of BAT adipocytes

BAT <- readRDS("mouse_snRNAseq_singlet_removeMTRPHB_BAT_sub_scVI.RDS")

new.cluster.ids <- c("Brown adipocyte", "White adipocyte")
names(new.cluster.ids) <- levels(BAT)
